# Generic `skills/` at repo root is noise from unrelated tooling.
# Do NOT use `skills/` — it matches `.claude/skills/` too. If you need
# an ignore for a top-level `skills/` add `/skills/` (leading slash).
# Project Claude Code skills live in .claude/skills/ and are tracked.
/skills/

